Kyle Tu 101269161

Purpose: A program that simulates a pit game where 2 heros randomly move in a map with 
randomly moving monsters and they try to escape without dying while ninjas rappel from
the top to try and pull them out.

Source Files: Escape.cc Hero.cc Participant.cc Snorc.cc Ninja.cc random.cc defs.h 
Escape.h Hero.h Participant.h Snorc.h Ninja.h MoveBehaviour.h EscapeeBehaviour.h
RescuerBehaviour.h VillainBehaviour.h RescuedBehaviour.h List.h random.h

Launch Instructions:-
1.)Have all files mentioned above in the same directory
2.)In terminal enter the following command in the same directory; "make"
3.)Now enter "./test" to run the program